At Family Tree Arborists, we know that tree maintenance and removals can be expensive. We want to offer you the "family discount" at the most reasonable rates in London and surrounding areas. We have a very friendly staff who will book your FREE QUOTE at a time that is convenient for you. We have 15 years personal experience in professional tree removal, both residential and commercial. We have an elite team of Arborists who will use the utmost caution, skill and ingenuity to safely remove or trim any tree problem you may have. We are fully insured for up to two million dollars ($2,000,0000) liability to remove and trim trees on both residential and commercial propertieis. 

Firewood Picked Up is:
$25/quarter face cord; 8 cubic feet
$40/half face cord; 16 cubic feet
$70/face cord; 32 cubic feet
$20 extra for delivery if required

As a part of our going green, we use more eco-friendly methods to do get the job done, do quotes and plant trees in order to help London maintain its name as the Forest City. We even have a battery powered chainsaw!

To book your FREE ESTIMATE call Mark at 226-224-6397 or Bree at 226-224-9248 or
For Lawn care & cleaning call or text Wayne at 519-851-709o
